`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Energy_Channel
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'energy channel'

 This spell raises the caster's maximum hit points while at the same time
lowering their maximum mana. The maximum amount of hit points the caster may
gain is determined by their current constitution. The effect of this spell is
only temporary.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
